params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" AS \\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"DetParent_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"DetParent_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"DetParent_MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"DetParent_OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" as \\"Det_MANHOUR_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" as \\"Det_PS_EDITION\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", 'FM99,999,999,999,990.0999') || '/' || to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", 'FM99,999,999,999,990.0999') as \\"Det_PS_UNIT_QTY\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"Det_STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Det_EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Det_EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"Det_PS_SPOIL\\", " +" M_PS.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"Det_CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_LT_FLG\\" as \\"Det_PS_LT_FLG\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_FIXED_LT\\") as \\"Det_PS_FIXED_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LT\\") as \\"Det_PS_PROP_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Det_PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_REF_NO\\") as \\"Det_PS_REF_NO\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COST_UP_TYP\\" as \\"Det_COST_UP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" as \\"Det_MRP_EXP_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Parent, " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Comp, " +" M_PS M_PS " +"where " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" as \\"Det_MANHOUR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"DETCOMP_STOCK_UNIT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"Sub1Parent_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"Sub1Comp_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"Sub1_STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"Sub1Comp_STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Sub1_EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Sub1_EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_SPOIL\\", " +" M_PS.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"Sub1_CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_LT_FLG\\" as \\"Sub1_PS_LT_FLG\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_FIXED_LT\\") as \\"Sub1_PS_FIXED_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LT\\") as \\"Sub1_PS_PROP_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_REF_NO\\") as \\"Sub1_PS_REF_NO\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COST_UP_TYP\\" as \\"Sub1_COST_UP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" as \\"Sub1_MRP_EXP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"h_Sub1_MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Parent, " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Comp, " +" M_PS M_PS " +"where " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" '1' as kbn1, " +" '1' as kbn2, " +" PLANT_CD, " +" ITEM_CD, " +" PROC_CD, " +" PROC_NO, " +" PROC_NAME, " +" WS_CD, " +" MODIFY_COUNT as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PROC\\", " +" null as \\"ISSUE_ITEM_CD\\", " +" null as \\"PS_EDITION\\", " +" null as \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" null as \\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_ISSUE\\", " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PS\\", " +" 0 as \\"PS_REF_NO\\", " +" ( " +" select " +" min(PROC_NO) " +" from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +" where " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" and ITEM_CD = ? " +" ) as \\"FIRST_PROC_NO\\" " +"from " +" ( " +" select " +" PLANT_CD, " +" ITEM_CD, " +" PROC_CD, " +" PROC_NO, " +" PROC_NAME, " +" WS_CD, " +" MODIFY_COUNT " +" from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +" where " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" and ITEM_CD = ? " +" ) t1, " +" ( " +" select " +" min(PARENT_ITEM_CD) as PARENT_ITEM_CD " +" from " +" M_PS " +" where " +" PARENT_ITEM_CD = ? " +" and TO_CHAR(EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') <= ? " +" and TO_CHAR(EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') >= ? " +" ) t2 " +"where " +" t1.ITEM_CD = t2.PARENT_ITEM_CD(+) " +"union all " +"SELECT " +" '2' as kbn1, " +" '1' as kbn2, " +" null, " +" M_PS.PARENT_ITEM_CD, " +" null, " +" null, " +" null, " +" null, " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PROC\\", " +" M_PS.COMP_ITEM_CD, " +" M_PS.PS_EDITION, " +" to_char(M_PS.EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" to_char(M_PS.EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_ISSUE\\", " +" M_PS.MODIFY_COUNT as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PS\\", " +" M_PS.PS_REF_NO as \\"PS_REF_NO\\", " +" 0 as \\"FIRST_PROC_NO\\" " +"from " +" M_PS " +"where " +" TO_CHAR(M_PS.EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') <= ? " +" and TO_CHAR(M_PS.EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') >= ? " +" and M_PS.PARENT_ITEM_CD = ? " +"order by " +" kbn1, " +" PROC_NO, " +" PS_REF_NO, " +" ISSUE_ITEM_CD"

"SELECT " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" AS \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" AS \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" AS \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" AS \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"FIXED_LT\\" AS \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LT\\" AS \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"SAFETY_LT\\" AS \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" AS \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"SPOIL\\" AS \\"SPOIL\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" AS \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" AS \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\" AS \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" AS \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" AS \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" M_PROC_GRP(\\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PROC_CD\\", \\"PROC_NO\\", \\"PROC_NAME\\", \\"WS_CD\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"FIXED_LT\\", \\"PROP_LT\\", \\"SAFETY_LT\\", \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", \\"SPOIL\\", \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", \\"STANDARD_COST\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?))"

"UPDATE " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"SET " +" \\"PROC_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"PROC_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"WS_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"FIXED_LT\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"PROP_LT\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"SAFETY_LT\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"SPOIL\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"STANDARD_COST\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" AS \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" AS \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" AS \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" AS \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OPR_RSLT_TYP\\" AS \\"OPR_RSLT_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"FIXED_LT\\" AS \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"PROP_LT\\" AS \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') AS \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ISSUE_LT\\" AS \\"ISSUE_LT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SAFETY_LT\\" AS \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" AS \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" AS \\"PROC_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY"
"SELECT " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" AS \\"WS_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_WS " +"WHERE " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"
"DELETE FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"DELETE FROM " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"WHERE " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"DELETE FROM " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"WHERE " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" AS \\"WS_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_WS " +"WHERE " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_WS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" AS \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" AS \\"PROC_NO\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" AS \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\") AS \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" AS \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" AS \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"FIXED_LT\\") AS \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LT\\") AS \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SAFETY_LT\\") AS \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') AS \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') AS \\"SPOIL\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" AS \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" AS \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') AS \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"UNIT_QTY\\" AS \\"UNIT_QTY\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WORK_TIME\\" AS \\"WORK_TIME\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" AS \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" AS \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +"FOR UPDATE NOWAIT"

"SELECT " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" AS \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" AS \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" AS \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"FIXED_LT\\" AS \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LT\\" AS \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"SAFETY_LT\\" AS \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" AS \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"SPOIL\\" AS \\"SPOIL\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" AS \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" AS \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\" AS \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" AS \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" AS \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" M_PROC_GRP.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" '2' as \\"kbn1\\", " +" '1' as \\"kbn2\\", " +" null as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" COMP_ITEM_CD as \\"Upper_ITEM_CD\\", " +" null as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" null as \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" null as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" null as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PROC\\", " +" PARENT_ITEM_CD as \\"Lower_ITEM_CD\\", " +" PS_EDITION as \\"PS_EDITION\\", " +" to_char(EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" to_char(EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_ISSUE\\", " +" MODIFY_COUNT as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PS\\", " +" PS_REF_NO as \\"PS_REF_NO\\" " +"from " +" M_PS " +"where " +" COMP_ITEM_CD = ? " +" and TO_CHAR(EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') <= ? " +" and TO_CHAR(EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') >= ? " +"union all " +"SELECT " +" '1' as \\"kbn1\\", " +" '1' as \\"kbn2\\", " +" t2.PLANT_CD, " +" t2.ITEM_CD as \\"Upper_ITEM_CD\\", " +" t2.PROC_CD, " +" t2.PROC_NO, " +" t2.PROC_NAME, " +" t2.WS_CD, " +" t2.MODIFY_COUNT as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PROC\\", " +" t2.ITEM_CD as \\"Lower_ITEM_CD\\", " +" null as \\"PS_EDITION\\", " +" null as \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" null as \\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_ISSUE\\", " +" 0 as \\"MODIFY_CNT_PS\\", " +" null as \\"PS_REF_NO\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP t2 " +"where " +" t2.ITEM_CD = ? " +" and t2.PLANT_CD = ? " +"order by " +" \\"kbn1\\", " +" \\"Lower_ITEM_CD\\", " +" \\"PROC_NO\\""

"SELECT " +" M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\" AS \\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\" AS \\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PS " +"WHERE " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"
